stagram.com/reel/DElYFY_SJQ6/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>上写道：“心碎得无以言表”。 “和家人坐在一起，看新闻，在电视直播中看到我们在马里布的家被烧毁，这是任何人都不应该经历的事情。这个家是我们建立许多珍贵回忆的地方”。</p><p>因主演<em>《公主新娘</em>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/saw-cary-elwes-interview-anniversary-2562185"><em>电锯惊魂</em></a>》而闻名的加利·艾尔维斯<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DElRwIfSFtz/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在他的 Instagram 帐户上写道</a>：“遗憾的是我们确实失去了家园，但我们很庆幸能够在这场真正毁灭性的火灾中幸存下来”。</p><p>奥斯卡获奖演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-woods-breaks-down-in-tears-after-house-destroyed-by-wildfires-3827444">詹姆斯·伍兹在接受电视直播采访时泪流满面</a>，详细描述了他的疏散和失去家园的情况。 “有一天你在游泳池里游泳，第二天一切就都消失了，”他说。他还回忆起他八岁的侄女天真的提供的帮助，心情崩溃了。 “她带着她的小雪人存钱罐出来了，让我们重建我们的房子，”他一边擦眼泪一边说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3827991" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827991" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827991" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270.jpg" alt="消防员继续扑灭洛杉矶帕利塞兹大火" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827991" class="wp-caption-text">消防队员继续与洛杉矶帕利塞兹大火作斗争。图片来源：CAL FIRE 的官方 Flickr 帐户/讲义/Anadolu，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-diivs-zachary-cole-smith-after-losing-home-in-la-wildfires-3827362">DIIV 乐队主唱扎卡里·科尔·史密斯 (Zachary Cole Smith) 的房屋因火灾而发起</a>筹款活动。据他们的朋友 Lindsey Hartman 发起的<a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-dani-cole-and-roy-smith-rebuild?attribution_id=sl:75f5dc00-a217-461b-afe9-47c579cfd15e&amp;utm_campaign=fp_sharesheet&amp;utm_medium=customer&amp;utm_source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GoFundMe 活动</a>称，史密斯和他的家人很安全，但不幸的是他们的房子在火灾中被烧毁。</p><p>哈特曼写道：“丹妮还怀孕六个月，这让这起可怕的事件变得更加难以承受。这个家包括他们所有的财产（衣服、传家宝、珍贵的财产）以及科尔的所有音乐装备、家用汽车，以及为罗伊和即将出生的新生儿提供的所有婴儿用品。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德</a>等音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">很快在社交媒体上分享了资源链接，而其他人则详细介绍了他们的疏散经历</a>。其他人也向遭受悲剧影响的人们表示同情，因为成千上万的房屋、财物等被烧毁。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joe-bonamassa-confirms-collection-of-vintage-guitar-gear-one-of-the-largest-in-the-world-is-safe-from-la-wildfires-3828023">Joe Bonamassa 确认收藏的古董吉他装备（世界上最大的吉他装备之一）不会受到洛杉矶野火的影响，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《阿诺拉》导演的母亲不同意这部电影的剧本：“人们不想看到这个” https://www.nme.com/news/film/anora-directors-mother-disapproved-of-the-films-script-people-dont-want-to-see-that-3828019?ut m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=anora-导演-母亲-不赞成-电影-脚本-人们不想看-那个Chris EdwardsFri, 10 Jan 2025 19:27:47 +0000 Film NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3828019 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·贝克和麦基·麦迪逊" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “放心，我妈妈会看你的评论的”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anora-directors-mother-disapproved-of-the-films-script-people-dont-want-to-see-that-3828019">《Anora》导演的母亲不同意该电影的剧本：“人们不想看到这个”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·贝克和麦基·麦迪逊" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_seanbaker_mikeymadison_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont