在洛杉矶野火中失去家园后，为 Empress Of 及其家人发起筹款活动https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-empress-of-and-family-after-losing-home-in-la-wildfires-3827984?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fundraiser-为在拉野火中失去家园的皇后及其家人发射Liberty DunworthFri, 10 Jan 2025 16:55:46 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3827984 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="歌手皇后登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “请帮助这个家庭向周围的人展示他们一直以来的爱和支持”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-empress-of-and-family-after-losing-home-in-la-wildfires-3827984">在洛杉矶野火中失去家园后为 Empress Of 及其家人发起的筹款活动</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="歌手皇后登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在洛杉矶持续的山火中失去家园后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/empress-of">Empress Of</a>及其家人发起了一项筹款活动。</p><p>这所房子的主人是 Empress Of（真名 Lorely Rodriguez），她的母亲 Reyna 是周二（1 月 7 日）洛杉矶发生的火灾中的众多房屋之一。</p><p>火灾很快在不同的社区发展为五场同时发生的火灾，到目前为止，已有超过 18 万居民被迫撤离家园。据<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/weather/wildfires/live-blog/california-wildfires-live-updates-deadly-blazes-spread-hollywood-hills-rcna186927" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NBC 新闻</em></a>报道，截至撰写本文时，已确认 10 人死亡。</p><p>现在， <a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-empress-of-her-family-after-home-lost-in-eaton-fire?attribution_id=sl:8576c676-fa87-45d3-ba48-b58fcbab7616&amp;utm_campaign=fp_sharesheet&amp;utm_medium=customer&amp;utm_source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一项筹款活动已经启动，</a>以帮助支持这位音乐家和她的家人，因为已证实他们“失去了一切”。</p><p> GoFundMe 上的描述写道：“两天前，我们亲爱的朋友 Lorely Rodriguez 和她的母亲 Reyna 失去了位于阿尔塔迪纳的房子，我们请求您的帮助，为他们筹集资金。” “你们中有些人可能知道 Lorely 是皇后。她是我们洛杉矶社区的一位音乐家。她也是一个女儿，也是一个现在失去一切的家庭中的兄弟姐妹。” </p><figure id="attachment_3827988" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827988" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827988" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of-screenshot@2000.jpg" alt="Empress Of Instagram Stories 的屏幕截图，显示了洛杉矶野火造成的损失" width="1600" height="2860" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of-screenshot@2000.jpg 1600w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of-screenshot@2000-400x715.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of-screenshot@2000-800x1430.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of-screenshot@2000-696x1244.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of-screenshot@2000-1392x2488.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/empress-of-screenshot@2000-1068x1909.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827988" class="wp-caption-text"> Empress Of Instagram Stories 的屏幕截图，显示了野火造成的损坏。图片来源：@empressof/Instagram</figcaption></figure><p> “几十年来，雷娜的家一直是洛雷利和她的兄弟姐妹的家庭中心，但在阿尔塔迪纳的火灾中不幸被毁。这意味着这个家庭的四名成员现在无家可归，”它补充道。 “由于没有时间收拾行李，一家人需要衣服、床上用品、食物、临时住房和金钱来重建生活。”</p><p> “多年来，Lorely 通过她的善良、音乐和艺术为社区做出了无尽的贡献，就像 Reyna 所做的那样。 Reyna 在 Instagram 上又名“Latina Knowles”，多年来一直为 Lorely 缝制舞台服装。所有人都在他们深爱的房子里进行设计和集思广益。请帮助我们筹集这些资金，并向这个家庭展示他们一直以来对周围人的爱和支持。”</p><p>在撰写本文时，已经向筹款活动捐款，筹集了6369美元（39,267英镑）的65,000美元（53,290英镑）的目标。 <a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-empress-of-her-family-after-home-lost-in-eaton-fire?attribution_id=sl:8576c676-fa87-45d3-ba48-b58fcbab7616&amp;utm_campaign=fp_sharesheet&amp;utm_medium=customer&amp;utm_source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问这里</a>以了解更多信息并捐款。女皇还在社交媒体上分享了该页面以及损害的图像（上）。</p><p> Empress的最新专辑以“供您的考虑”形式出现在2023年。这是她的第四家工作室LP，也是2020年代“我是您的“我是您的&#39;和2022 EP <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empress-of-returns-with-dramatic-new-single-save-me-3202183">” Save Me&#39;</a>的后续行动，并包含<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empress-of-teams-up-with-rina-sawayama-for-new-single-kiss-me-3503922">Rina Sawayama的单曲“ Kiss Me”。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3827991" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827991" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827991" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270.jpg" alt="消防员继续与洛杉矶的帕利萨德（Palisades）火灾作斗争" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/la-wildfires@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827991" class="wp-caption-text">消防员继续与洛杉矶的帕利萨德（Palisades）消防作斗争。信用：Cal Fire / Dentout / Anadolu通过Getty Images的官方Flickr帐户</figcaption></figure><p>在受野火影响的房屋中，有喜剧演员和演员比利·克里斯塔尔（Billy Crystal），卡里·埃尔维斯（Cary Elwes），<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡金像奖</a>得主<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-woods-breaks-down-in-tears-after-house-destroyed-by-wildfires-3827444">詹姆斯·伍兹（James Woods）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars">《星球大战传奇》（Star Wars Woods）</a>传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-hamill">马克·哈米尔（Mark Hamill）</a> 。</p><p><em>英雄</em>和<em>这是我们</em>演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/heroes-star-milo-ventimiglia-chokes-up-after-watching-house-burn-down-in-la-wildfires-your-heart-just-breaks-3827763">米洛·文蒂米利亚（Milo Ventimiglia）在现场采访中也cho住了，讨论看着他的房子被烧毁时</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-diivs-zachary-cole-smith-after-losing-home-in-la-wildfires-3827362">Diiv的主持人扎卡里·科尔·史密斯（Zachary Cole Smith）的筹款活动是在他的房子屈服于大火之后发起的</a>。</p><p>根据他们的朋友林赛·哈特曼（Lindsey Hartman）发起的后者的<a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-dani-cole-and-roy-smith-rebuild?attribution_id=sl:75f5dc00-a217-461b-afe9-47c579cfd15e&amp;utm_campaign=fp_sharesheet&amp;utm_medium=customer&amp;utm_source=copy_link">Gofundme运动</a>，史密斯和他的家人很安全，但不幸的是，他们的房屋被烧毁并在大火中被摧毁。</p><p>昨天（1月9日），<a href="/artists/paris-hilton">巴黎希尔顿</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paris-hilton-and-billy-crystal-among-hollywood-stars-to-lose-homes-in-la-wildfires-3827526">分享了她看着自己在电视上燃烧的房屋燃烧的经历</a>，好莱坞传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anthony-hopkins">安东尼·霍普金斯爵士</a>成为最新失去家园的人之一。</p><p>许多<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">音乐家和演员对野火表达了悲伤</a>，并提供了包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a>在内的支持。</p><p>今天（1月10日）早些时候（1月10日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/suspected-arsonist-arrested-in-connection-with-new-la-blaze-3827860">逮捕了与正在进行的大火有关的</a>人，该人涉嫌在西山地区开始肯尼斯大火。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fundraiser-launched-for-empress-of-and-family-after-losing-home-in-la-wildfires-3827984">在La Wildfires失去家园后，邮政筹款活动</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现在La Wildfires之后。</p> ;
 Lumineers 宣布为 War Child 举办一场惊喜、亲密的伦敦演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lumineers-announce-intimate-london-show-for-war-child-buy-tickets-3827958?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-lumineers-announce-亲密伦敦演出为战争儿童买票Liberty DunworthFri, 10 Jan 2025 15:58:43 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3827958 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lumineers 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周早些时候，两人公布了新专辑《Automatic》的详细信息</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lumineers-announce-intimate-london-show-for-war-child-buy-tickets-3827958">The Lumineers 宣布为 War Child 举办的令人惊喜、亲密的伦敦演出</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lumineers 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lumineers@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lumineers">Lumineers 乐队</a>分享了在伦敦举办的一场令人惊喜的亲密演出的细节，其资金将捐给“战争儿童”。了解以下详细信息。</p><p>今天（1 月 10 日）宣布，即将举行的一次性演出将于本月晚些时候在伦敦霍克斯顿大厅举行。这场演出将于 1 月 17 日举行，这将是这对美国独立组合自本周早些时候宣布新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lumineers-announce-fifth-album-automatic-with-soaring-new-single-same-old-song-3827039">Automatic</a> 》消息以来的首场演出。</p><p>对于即将到来的演出，乐队与<a href="https://www.warchild.org.uk/donate-gazaemergencyappeal-2024-paidsearch?gad_source=1&amp;gclid=CjwKCAiAp4O8BhAkEiwAqv2UqBcS-3PJs50Djvj34suYzfxjuJjquqLAGu0ECRDmOlmsoreldRmbeRoCWPYQAvD_BwE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">War Child</a>合作，这意味着演出筹集的资金将用于帮助生活在冲突地区的儿童。</p><p> “我们非常感谢 The Lumineers 和他们的团队贡献了时间和才华来帮助我们筹集资金，我相信这将在霍克斯顿大厅举办一场精美而亲密的演出，粉丝们将会享受到真正的享受，”克莱尔War Child 现场音乐主管桑德斯·赖特 (Sanders-Wright) 在一份新声明中表示。 </p><figure id="attachment_3827962" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827962" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827962" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LUMINEERS@2000X2000.jpg" alt="Lumineers 霍克斯顿大厅巡演海报，2025 年。" width="2000" height="2842" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LUMINEERS@2000X2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LUMINEERS@2000X2000-400x568.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LUMINEERS@2000X2000-800x1137.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LUMINEERS@2000X2000-696x989.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LUMINEERS@2000X2000-1392x1978.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LUMINEERS@2000X2000-1068x1518.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827962" class="wp-caption-text"> Lumineers 霍克斯顿大厅巡演海报，2025 年。图片来源：出版社</figcaption></figure><p>“任何儿童都不应该成为战争的一部分，过去的一年尤其可怕，这意味着我们的工作需要得到 Lumineers 及其团队以及所有捐赠者的更多支持，”桑德斯-赖特持续。 “筹集的每一分钱都有助于我们为世界各地陷入冲突地区的儿童提供急需的紧急援助、心理支持、教育等。”</p><p>霍克斯顿厅特别演出的门票将通过抽奖获得—— <a href="https://www.universe.com/events/the-lumineers-intimate-charity-show-in-aid-of-war-child-tickets-Y81XB2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>购买选票，就有机会赢得一对演出门票。投票将于周二（1 月 14 日）晚上 11:59 截止，获奖者将在演出前 48 小时收到通知。</p><p>下周的亲密演出将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lumineers-announce-2025-uk-and-european-arena-tour-buy-tickets-3797146">The Lumineers 今年 5 月开始英国和爱尔兰巡回演出</a>之前进行，其中包括在伦敦 O2 的一场演出。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/the-lumineers-tickets/artist/1498863?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xOnTBHWu7xyKRF4SKGSfxVZQUks0hQQFGVH-Tg0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559">在这里找到所有剩余的门票</a>并查看下面的日期列表。</p><h2> <strong>Lumineers 2025 年英国和爱尔兰巡演日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>可能</strong><br /><strong>22 - 卡迪夫竞技场，卡迪夫</strong><br /><strong>24 – O2，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>25 - AO 竞技场，曼彻斯特</strong><br /><strong>28 - 伯明翰Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>29 – 格拉斯哥海德鲁竞技场</strong><br /><strong>31 - 圣安妮公园，都柏林</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Lumineers - 同样的老歌（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cZ-VW3QYQQA?start=2&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>如前所述，The Lumineers 本周早些时候宣布了他们即将推出的第五张录音室专辑“Automatic”的详细信息，并预览了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lumineers-announce-fifth-album-automatic-with-soaring-new-single-same-old-song-3827039">主打单曲“Same Old Song”的 LP。</a></p><p>成员 Wesley Schultz 和 Jeremiah Fraites 将于 2 月 14 日通过 Dualtone 分享 11 首曲目的记录 -<a href="https://thelumineers.lnk.to/automatic" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订/预保存</a>。</p><p>继 2022 年的《Brightside》之后，乐队解释说，这张唱片“标志着歌曲创作的 20 年”，并将探索“现代世界的一些荒谬之处，比如真实与虚假之间的界限越来越模糊，以及我们用各种方式麻痹自己，同时试图对抗无聊和过度刺激。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bruce-springsteen-and-zach-bryan-perform-atlantic-city-together-in-philadelphia-3782210">去年 8 月，The Lumineers 乐队与 Bruce Springsteen 和 Zach Bryan 一起现场表演了 Bryan 2020 年专辑《Elisabeth》中的《Revival》</a> ，随后发布了一系列新消息。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lumineers-announce-intimate-london-show-for-war-child-buy-tickets-3827958">The Lumineers 宣布为 War Child 举办的令人惊喜、亲密的伦敦演出</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
